MAIN PARTS
  - Electric scooter frame (or secondhand electric scooter)
  - Brushless DC motor
  - Battery Module (Li-ion or LiFePo4)
  - ESC
  - Buck/boost converter

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ESC COMPONENTS
  1. Microcontroller (Arduino Nano)
  2. N-type MOSFETS
  3. MOSFET gate driver IC
  4. DC-DC buck/boost converter
  5. Heat sink
  6. Aluminum case
  7. Resistors
  8. Capacitors (ceramic and electrolytic)
  9. Switches and button
  10. LEDs
  11. PCB terminals
  12. Fuse
  13. Diodes
  14. Pin headers

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TESTING EQUIPMENT
  1. ESC
  2. BLDC motor
  3. Battery
  4. Electric scooter
  5. Oscilloscope and data logger
  6. Tachometer
